    <outline text="Bradley Beal — Hip fracture requiring season-ending surgery (2026-06-25)" type="link" url="https://www.nba.com/news/clippers-bradley-beal-out-season-hip-fracture" description="Clippers lose a veteran guard for the balance of the season and into next year's planning"/>
