    <outline text="Harshit Rana — Hamstring injury sustained during the third T20I vs. England at Trent Bridge (2026-07-09)" type="link" url="https://ianslive.in/4th-t20i-injured-rana-chakaravarthy-ruled-out-of-remaining-games-against-england--20260709215924" description="Deepens India's bowling injury crisis on the England tour, with Rana joining Varun Chakaravarthy, Hardik Pandya, and Nitish Kumar Reddy on the unavailable list"/>
