    <outline text="Manuel Ugarte — Knee ligament injury suffered vs. Spain at the World Cup; possible cruciate ligament (ACL) damage (2026-06-28)" type="link" url="https://www.premierleague.com/en/latest-player-injuries" description="Would be a significant blow to Manchester United's midfield depth heading into 2026-27"/>
    <outline text="Rodri — Undisclosed injury expected to require surgery after the World Cup (2026-06-27)" type="link" url="https://www.premierleague.com/en/latest-player-injuries" description="Manchester City to start the new season without their midfield anchor"/>
    <outline text="Matthijs de Ligt — Surgery on a long-standing back injury (2026-06-20)" type="link" url="https://www.premierleague.com/en/latest-player-injuries" description="United lose a starting center-back for an extended stretch"/>
    <outline text="Chris Richards — Torn ankle ligaments (two ligaments) suffered vs. Brentford (2026-06-15)" type="link" url="https://www.premierleague.com/en/latest-player-injuries" description="Crystal Palace lose a starting center-back for a multi-week stretch"/>
    <outline text="Chloe Ricketts — Ankle injury (2026-06-15)" type="link" url="https://www.spotrac.com/nwsl/injured/_/year/2026" description="Boston Legacy FC without a rostered defender for at least 45 days"/>
