  <outline text="Tennis">
    <outline text="Matteo Berrettini — Diagnosed with chronic hip pain, a recurrence of the left hip issue that forced his retirement from his Roland Garros quarterfinal in early June (2026-07-07)" type="link" url="https://www.puntodebreak.com/en/2026/07/07/berrettini-withdraws-from-competing-in-upcoming-tournaments-due-to-chronic-hip-pain" description="Removes him from the draw at both tournaments immediately following his third-round Wimbledon loss to Grigor Dimitrov"/>
